system.effect: Prerequisites: Minor Gift - Seamaster Daily - Standard Action Target: Self Effect: For the next three rounds, foes within 6 meters of  you do not gain the benefits of Rain Dance. Their Water  Type Moves do not deal extra damage, Hurricane and  Thunder retain their usual Accuracy Check, Abilities  based on Rainy Weather do not activate, and Moves  such as Weather Ball do not gain added benefit. All  detrimental effects of Rain Dance still apply.
